#explain
  .explain-container.d-flex.flex-column.h-100
    .top-bar.btn-toolbar.options-toolbar.bg-light.flex-shrink-0(role="toolbar")
      include ../../font-size
      .ai-disclaimer.text-muted.small.mx-2(title="AI-generated explanations may contain errors or inaccuracies")
        i.fas.fa-info-circle.me-1
        | AI may be inaccurate
      .explain-options.d-flex.mx-2
        .explain-option-group.me-2
          label.form-label.small.mb-0.me-1 Audience:
          select.explain-audience.form-select.form-select-sm.explain-select(style="width: auto;")
            option(value="loading") Loading...
        .explain-option-group.me-2
          label.form-label.small.mb-0.me-1 Focus:
          select.explain-type.form-select.form-select-sm.explain-select(style="width: auto;")
            option(value="loading") Loading...
      .status.ms-auto
        i.status-icon.fas.d-none
    .explain-consent.d-none.flex-shrink-0
      p.mb-0 Claude Explain will send your code and compilation output to an external API. Continue?
      button.btn.btn-primary.mt-2.consent-btn Yes, explain this code
    .explain-content.content.markdown-body.flex-grow-1.overflow-auto
    .bottom-bar.bg-light.d-none.explain-bottom-bar.flex-shrink-0.px-3.d-flex.align-items-center
      button.btn.btn-sm.btn-link.explain-reload(title="Regenerate explanation")
        i.fas.fa-sync-alt
      span.explain-stats.ms-auto